@mbien I think it is related to JPMS, NB cache and refactoring. I will explain why I think so. I've noticed that when I clear NB cache and everything is OK, no errors are shown in NB, all code is compiled and works. Then I start refactoring. If I change key classes/interfaces I can get something like this in my tests:

![Screenshot from 2024-02-21 12-05-45](https://github.com/apache/netbeans/assets/10261361/76d6eca9-8788-4431-b1aa-edf9eb15f2da)

NB says that some modules are not imported, but it is false as if I clear cache again, then everything is OK. Besides renaming stops working at some point. I work only with JPMS.
